# - Try to find Freetype2
# Once done this will define
#
#  FREETYPE_FOUND - system has Freetype2
#  FREETYPE_INCLUDES - the Freetype2 include directory
#  FREETYPE_LIBRARIES - The libraries needed to use Freetype2
